---
// 服务介绍组件
---

<section id="services" class="services-section py-5xl">
  <div class="container">
    
    <!-- 标题区域 -->
    <div class="section-header text-center mb-5xl">
      <div class="section-number">
        <span class="accent-number">02</span>
        <div class="english-text small-element opacity-70">Services</div>
      </div>
      <h2 class="section-title chinese-text">
        以道为本
        <br />
        <span class="english-text font-light opacity-80">Rooted in Wisdom</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="section-description chinese-text text-lg opacity-90 mt-xl">
        秉承「和光同尘」之道，在变化中寻找平衡，在复杂中发现简单
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <!-- 服务网格 -->
    <div class="services-grid grid grid-3 gap-xl">
      
      <!-- 咨询服务 -->
      <div class="service-card card fade-in-up">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <span class="large-element">智</span>
          <div class="english-text small-element">Consulting</div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="service-title chinese-text font-bold text-2xl mb-md">
          战略咨询
        </h3>
        <p class="service-description chinese-text mb-lg">
          融合东方智慧与现代管理理念，为企业提供深度战略规划与执行指导
        </p>
        <div class="service-features">
          <div class="feature english-text small-element opacity-70">• Strategic Planning</div>
          <div class="feature english-text small-element opacity-70">• Business Development</div>
          <div class="feature english-text small-element opacity-70">• Market Analysis</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- 技术服务 -->
      <div class="service-card card fade-in-up">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <span class="large-element">创</span>
          <div class="english-text small-element">Innovation</div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="service-title chinese-text font-bold text-2xl mb-md">
          技术创新
        </h3>
        <p class="service-description chinese-text mb-lg">
          以技术为载体，以创新为驱动，打造符合时代发展的数字化解决方案
        </p>
        <div class="service-features">
          <div class="feature english-text small-element opacity-70">• Digital Transformation</div>
          <div class="feature english-text small-element opacity-70">• Software Development</div>
          <div class="feature english-text small-element opacity-70">• AI Integration</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- 文化服务 -->
      <div class="service-card card fade-in-up">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <span class="large-element">和</span>
          <div class="english-text small-element">Harmony</div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="service-title chinese-text font-bold text-2xl mb-md">
          文化融合
        </h3>
        <p class="service-description chinese-text mb-lg">
          促进不同文化间的理解与合作，构建包容性的全球化商业生态
        </p>
        <div class="service-features">
          <div class="feature english-text small-element opacity-70">• Cross-cultural Communication</div>
          <div class="feature english-text small-element opacity-70">• International Cooperation</div>
          <div class="feature english-text small-element opacity-70">• Cultural Bridge Building</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
    </div>
    
    <!-- 核心价值观 -->
    <div class="values-section mt-5xl">
      <div class="values-grid grid grid-4 gap-lg">
        <div class="value-item text-center">
          <div class="value-number accent-number font-black">1</div>
          <div class="value-text chinese-text font-semibold">包容</div>
          <div class="value-subtitle english-text small-element opacity-70">Inclusivity</div>
        </div>
        <div class="value-item text-center">
          <div class="value-number accent-number font-black">2</div>
          <div class="value-text chinese-text font-semibold">智慧</div>
          <div class="value-subtitle english-text small-element opacity-70">Wisdom</div>
        </div>
        <div class="value-item text-center">
          <div class="value-number accent-number font-black">3</div>
          <div class="value-text chinese-text font-semibold">创新</div>
          <div class="value-subtitle english-text small-element opacity-70">Innovation</div>
        </div>
        <div class="value-item text-center">
          <div class="value-number accent-number font-black">4</div>
          <div class="value-text chinese-text font-semibold">和谐</div>
          <div class="value-subtitle english-text small-element opacity-70">Harmony</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .services-section {
    background: 
      radial-gradient(circle at 80% 20%, rgba(87, 81, 213, 0.03) 0%, transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 20% 80%, rgba(22, 22, 21, 0.02) 0%, transparent 50%);
  }
  
  .section-header {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .section-number {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }
  
  .section-number .accent-number {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }
  
  .section-description {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  
  .services-grid {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-20);
  }
  
  .service-card {
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border: 1px solid rgba(87, 81, 213, 0.1);
  }
  
  .service-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    transform: translateY(-8px);
  }
  
  .service-icon {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .service-icon .large-element {
    display: block;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
    text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(87, 81, 213, 0.2);
  }
  
  .service-title {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }
  
  .service-description {
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }
  
  .service-features {
    text-align: left;
    padding-left: var(--space-6);
  }
  
  .service-features .feature {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  /* 核心价值观样式 */
  .values-section {
    padding-top: var(--space-20);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(22, 22, 21, 0.1);
  }
  
  .value-item {
    padding: var(--space-6);
  }
  
  .value-number {
    font-size: var(--text-6xl);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    opacity: 0.8;
  }
  
  .value-text {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }
  
  .value-subtitle {
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }
  
  /* 响应式设计 */
  @media (max-width: 1200px) {
    .services-grid {
      gap: var(--space-6);
    }
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .services-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-8);
    }
    
    .values-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: var(--space-8);
    }
    
    .service-features {
      text-align: center;
      padding-left: 0;
    }
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .values-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-6);
    }
    
    .value-number {
      font-size: var(--text-5xl);
    }
  }
  
  /* 动画延迟 */
  .service-card:nth-child(1) {
    animation-delay: 0.1s;
  }
  
  .service-card:nth-child(2) {
    animation-delay: 0.2s;
  }
  
  .service-card:nth-child(3) {
    animation-delay: 0.3s;
  }
</style>